<h4>Required Reading:</h4>

<a href="http://www.wnet.org/fom/index.html"> <b>The Future of
Money</b></a>, a tutorial on Digital Economics by <a
href="http://www.wnet.org">Thirteen/WNET</a>, a non-profit organization
associated with the PBS television network.  Please read through at least
the <a href="http://www.wnet.org/fom/overview/index.html">overview</a>
